                                  BUSINESS QUESTION
Do higher transaction amounts increase fraud risk? 

                                 QUERY
SELECT
CASE 
WHEN amount > 3000 THEN 'High transaction'
ELSE 'Low transaction'
END AS Transaction_category,
COUNT(*) Fraud_count
FROM fraud_detection_data
GROUP BY Transaction_category;

                                Insight:
Lower transaction amounts experience more fraud cases, possibly because smaller transactions attract less suspicion and are harder to detect quickly.

                            Recommendation:
Implement strict verification for low-value transactions such as one time passcode 
